   182	| `SchemaProbe`      | `SchemaInconsistent`    | `TableRow { table: &'static str, rowid: i64 }`, `MigrationStep { from: u32, to: u32 }`, `OpaqueSqliteError { sqlite_extended_code: i32 }` | `E_CORRUPT_SCHEMA`            | `design/recovery.md#schema-inconsistent`     |
